'''Darrel Borsen''' was the Base Commander of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggling]] base on [[Danton VI]]. He was in command when a local disease caused the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]] to quarantine the entire planet. When a group of Rebels came to the planet, he instructed them to contact Imperial [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] captain [[Julias Narn]] to help them retrieve the antidote which had been stolen by [[Galderian/Legends|Galderian]] [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]], as they were the only people in the system with enough firepower to take on the pirates.

